dct_description_sm: Coordinates approximate and based on Greenwich meridian.
Shows topography, settlements, roads, places of historical interest.
Features illustrations of 2 coats of arms, Israelites, and structures.
Drawn after Reuwich-Breydenbach with some changes.
Appears in Jansson's Illustriorum Hispaniae urbium tabulae. Amsterdam, 1657. Part II, Folio D.
